title: Stop #10 of 2006/2007 PBRJ Tour - Mont Avila, Quebec, Canada
description: The 2006/07 North American PBRJ tour dipped into double digits with our 10th stop finding us at Mont Avila, QC on Saturday, March 3rd, 2007. Music by Valient Thorr.
